Winform and Console applications using Socket to test Client and Server.  
Solution contains 4 projects:  

1.Common  
	Common used classes, like algorithms for encrypt and decrypt.  
2.Client 
	Use Socket to connect to server, and send/receive message  
3.Server
	Use Socket to bind and listen, send/receive message with Client connnected  
Both Server and Client use RSACryptoServiceProvider to encrypt and decrypt.	
	